Well I am considering joining the democrats, for the first time in my life and say impeach him.  Not for the reasons they purport but because if he wants to run rough shod over the Constitution and encourage governors and local officials to do likewise, then he has abandoned his oath of office and should be removed.   The individual liberty of We the People is the priority.   Government has no authority or power to control the people's right to work and to provide for themselves and their family.  What gives the government authority to decide who goes bankrupt and who doesn't.   This is the most fundamental right that our nation and all modern nations were established on, the right to work. The second is the free hand of the market.   If corporations are being run so poorly that they can't survive a recession,  they the need to go bankrupt and close.  That is the fundamentals of the very fabric of how society works. 
Now, if people want to stay home to stay safe, they have that right but no one has a right to deny a person their freedom to provide for themselves and their family.   It is the most fundamental right of human kind and no level of risk from any circumstance is sufficient to justify infringing on that right.  If people are dumb enough to go out and hang out with a bunch of sick people, then you have the right to do that.  If you are old or vulnerable or just dont want to get sick and want to self quarantine, then you have the freedom to do that.  What is 100% for sure is that no level of government has any authority to restrict the rights or freedoms of Americans, that is up to individual people as to what they want to do and to be as reckless or careful as they choose with their own life.   Nearly every male  member of my family since the revolution has fought for this nation in war.  I will be dammed if they gave up everything for the hope of freedom FROM government just to have the fourth reich roll in now off a disease that is not even as dangerous as a common flu.  
Appreciate the help with getting people medical supplies but all the rest of the government assistance, no thank you.  I didn't ask for Trillions more in debt and the destruction of my future and my families future for people who didn't bother to take care of their bodies.  Obviously, I support the help being given to the elderly, but again, all the rest of the efforts are just blatant abuses of power and totally inappropriate for an educated people and society.  I don't appreciate the use of Patriotic language, just make the destruction of our rights seem like it is worthwhile.   Probably ten times more people are dying from the flu or most any other cause of death right now - this response has nothing to do with the seriousness of the virus.   Likely billions have had Covid19 and are fine, this could quite possibly be the least deadly disease know to man.  That puts the death rate at about . 0001% Sick of the fake news coming out of the corporate media.   Yes, we mourn for thoes who do get sick or perish but it dishonors every person who has fought for and died for this country to just throw away our freedoms for a disease that is one of the least dangerous known to man.  You know England wasn't even going to respond to the virus because it is so not dangerous - then a bunch of corrupt people in our government started calling over there and finally pressured them to start hyping it us like our corporate media.   Sick what they will do at the behest of BigPharma.  These are people's lives but to them, just another dollar sign.   As one Big Pharma executive said, "Curing people is not a sustainable business model."  They want you sick and looking to them to save you.  I will tell you what, there is one Savior and He doesn't wear a white coat, though He is clothed in white.  Who do you think they are trying to imitate?
